DESCRIPTION:Interledger Foundation fellowship funding individuals to advanc
 e open\, interoperable digital payment infrastructure (the Interledger Pro
 tocol and Open Payments) and broaden digital financial access. ELIGIBILITY
 : individual researchers\, developers\, open-source contributors\, advocat
 es\, creators and artists working on digital financial inclusion\; open wo
 rldwide. Apply via the Interledger fellowship page.\n\nOrganisation: Inter
 ledger Foundation\nLocation: Remote (worldwide)\nAward: USD 72\,000 person
 al stipend plus a USD 20\,000 project budget. No application fee.\nDuratio
 n: Fellowship term (project-based)\n\nMore: https://interledger.org/grant/
 fellowship?utm_source=artificialnouveaugrantdesk&utm_medium=referral
